law.text:
The following organizational units and administrative bodies shall be attached to the Office of the Governor:
Council on Postsecondary Education;
Foundation for Adult Education;
Department of Military Affairs;
Department for Local Government;
Early Childhood Advisory Council;
Kentucky Commission on Human Rights;
Kentucky Commission on Women;
Kentucky Commission on Military Affairs;
Agricultural Development Board;
Kentucky Agricultural Finance Corporation;
Office of Minority Empowerment;
The Martin Luther King Commission; and
Office of Homeland Security.
